  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/174c3a755271be6e51d58b42a3ad324d.poster.avif?t=1731743588\" width=540 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/174c3a755271be6e51d58b42a3ad324d.webm?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/174c3a755271be6e51d58b42a3ad324d.mp4?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Original car chase game is back! PAKO 3 brings insane amount of levels and cars to unlock, while keeping the simple gameplay. Transport your crew as a getaway driver, escape cops in survival levels, drive fast laps on racing levels and try capturing all areas in the Zones levels!<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br>+ 4 game modes: Getaway Driver, Racing, Survival, Zones<br>+ Choose camera view between isometric and 3rd person camera<br>+ Easy and addictive gameplay<br>+ 30+ levels and cars to unlock<br>+ Pick up bonus items to help your journey!<br>+ Unlock and paint cars<br>+ Pulsing synthwave soundtrack by DKSTR<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/c232360a9b3858f96863092b7973f848.poster.avif?t=1731743588\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/c232360a9b3858f96863092b7973f848.webm?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/c232360a9b3858f96863092b7973f848.mp4?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/174c3a755271be6e51d58b42a3ad324d.poster.avif?t=1731743588\" width=540 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/174c3a755271be6e51d58b42a3ad324d.webm?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/174c3a755271be6e51d58b42a3ad324d.mp4?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Original car chase game is back! PAKO 3 brings insane amount of levels and cars to unlock, while keeping the simple gameplay. Transport your crew as a getaway driver, escape cops in survival levels, drive fast laps on racing levels and try capturing all areas in the Zones levels!<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br>+ 4 game modes: Getaway Driver, Racing, Survival, Zones<br>+ Choose camera view between isometric and 3rd person camera<br>+ Easy and addictive gameplay<br>+ 30+ levels and cars to unlock<br>+ Pick up bonus items to help your journey!<br>+ Unlock and paint cars<br>+ Pulsing synthwave soundtrack by DKSTR<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/c232360a9b3858f96863092b7973f848.poster.avif?t=1731743588\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/c232360a9b3858f96863092b7973f848.webm?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915280/extras/c232360a9b3858f96863092b7973f848.mp4?t=1731743588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
